Description: Unofficial patches to provide a classic GTK3 experience
 GTK3 patched to provide a more classic experience. Includes CSD removal,
 traditional dialogs buttons and icons, and more appearance tweaks.
 .
 This package is 'monolithic' in the sense that it is a complete build of
 gtk+3.0, which is typically split into separate packages. It also cannot
 co-exist with the original gtk+3.0 packages.
 .
 This is provided WITHOUT ANY WARRANTY. If things break, install the
 original gtk+3.0 packages, or keep the broken pieces.
 .
 More information: https://github.com/lah7/gtk3-classic.git
